Acceptance: Treat successful Telegram Bot API getUpdates long polling over HTTPS with the configured bot token as the production trust boundary. Persist and advance update_id offsets monotonically, deduplicate replay across restart, bind identity to the configured bot/account namespace plus immutable from.id, distinguish private/chat context, and reject malformed, missing-user, bot, stale/replayed, cross-bot, or display-only evidence. Webhook secret-token verification remains a separate adapter if webhook ingress is enabled. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-13-github-user-attribution-and-feature-discovery.md.